{"type":null,"faqId":38954,"title":"荣耀手环zero敲击屏幕不亮怎么办？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\r\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>&nbsp;<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '微软雅黑', 'sans-serif'; COLOR: #000000; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">手环被固定的较紧（比如放在充电底座上）或者佩戴较紧时单击屏幕可能无法点亮；当您处于行走（走路）或跑步途中，这时敲击屏幕也无法点亮。您可以通过翻腕亮屏和抬腕亮屏的方式点亮屏幕。</span></p>\n<!--\n<div id=\"floatDiv\"></div>\n--></span></div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4264","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673016000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":227,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀手环zero,b0,zero,点亮屏幕,屏幕不亮,走路不亮,跑步不亮,敲击不亮","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}